  "title": "Sales Engineer (Valves/ Oil & Gas) - North - WCDT",
  "description": "<p><em><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></em></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Review project specifications and prepare sales quotations.</li>\n  <li>Provide pre-sales and technical support to customers.</li>\n  <li>Coordinate with internal departments to ensure timely delivery.</li>\n  <li>Undertake ad-hoc assignments as required.</li>\n  <li>Source and negotiate with mills and suppliers.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><em><strong>Requirements:</strong></em></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Minimum diploma or degree in any engineering discipline.</li>\n  <li>At least 3 to 5 years of internal sales experience, specifically in valve-related products within the oil &amp; gas, marine, or offshore industries (mandatory).</li>\n  <li>Strong interpersonal and communication skills.</li>\n  <li>Proficient in project management with a customer-focused mindset.</li>\n  <li>Highly detail-oriented, proactive, with strong follow-up and negotiation abilities.</li>\n  <li>Able to work effectively under pressure and meet tight deadlines.</li>\n  <li>Prior exposure to project management is an advantage.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>WECRUIT PTE LTD | 20C0270</p>\n<p>TEW JIE WEI | R22106822</p>",
